text: Jan Kuczyński (7 January 1935 - 28 November 2009) was a Polish wrestler. He competed in the men's freestyle lightweight at the 1960 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1935 births Category:2009 deaths Category:Polish male sport wrestlers Category:Olympic wrestlers of Poland Category:Wrestlers at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Vilnius Category:People from Wilno Voivodeship (1926–1939)
